The paper discusses a method for semantic search in e-commerce, which falls under the category of Information Retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also mentions the use of ontologies, which is a topic in Computational Linguistics (cs.CL) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the extraction of product classes, which involves data management (cs.DB) and machine learning (cs.LG).
